    {
      "name": "School of Illusion",
      "description": "Electronistu has chosen the School of Illusion as his Arcane Tradition, specializing in magic that deceives the senses and the mind."
    },
    {
      "name": "Illusion Savant",
      "description": "The gold and time spent to copy an Illusion spell into the spellbook is halved."
    },
    {
      "name": "Mark of the Deep Wood",
      "description": "A faint pattern of silver-green veins traces Electronistu's left forearm \u2014 the sigil of an ancient forest spirit. The debt has been paid, but a new pact has begun. The spirit's purpose remains unknown, but its power thrums beneath the skin, waiting."
    }
  ],
